00:00:14,040 --> 00:00:14,840
Lu Huai.

2
00:00:16,760 --> 00:00:18,160
I made you a bowl of sweet soup.

3
00:00:18,400 --> 00:00:19,160
Try it.

4
00:00:19,960 --> 00:00:21,560
It's made by the cook again, isn't it?

5
00:00:22,080 --> 00:00:22,840
No, it's not.

6
00:00:23,320 --> 00:00:25,080
I really made this myself.

7
00:00:26,120 --> 00:00:26,880
Just try it.

8
00:00:29,120 --> 00:00:30,320
Just say what's on your mind.

9
00:00:40,400 --> 00:00:41,440
You saved me from poison.

10
00:00:42,280 --> 00:00:44,480
This is my way of saying thank you.

11
00:00:48,160 --> 00:00:49,440
I burned my hand red

12
