when making the soup.

13
00:00:52,520 --> 00:00:53,320
Look.

14
00:00:56,120 --> 00:00:56,880
Su Yunqi.

15
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:58,520
Sometimes,

16
00:00:58,800 --> 00:01:00,800
I can't tell if you're acting.

17
00:01:06,440 --> 00:01:08,320
I wonder if you really
have feelings for me.

18
00:01:09,040 --> 00:01:09,640
I...

19
00:01:14,600 --> 00:01:15,160
Go hide.

20
00:01:26,960 --> 00:01:28,120
Hand over the thing.

21
00:01:28,240 --> 00:01:29,080
And I'll spare you.

22
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:30,920
Why don't you

23
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:32,120
come and take it?

24
00:01:43,616 --> 00:01:45,440
(Chapter 24)
(An arrow is shot from south.)

25
00:01:45,440 --> 00:01:47,280
(Su Luoluo takes the arrow for Lu Huai.)

26
00:01:47,480 --> 00:01:48,200
What?

27
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:50,360
Su Luoluo takes an arrow for Lu Huai?

28
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:53,000
How come I don't see Su Luoluo?

29
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:55,200
It was supposed to be her
who came to Lu's Mansion.

30
00:01:55,440 --> 00:01:57,720
But you recklessly changed the plot.

31
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:58,480
Cut the nonsense.

32
00:01:59,040 --> 00:02:00,840
What happens to him
now that she's not here?

33
00:02:01,720 --> 00:02:03,360
He'll die from the arrow.

34
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,760
No need to take an arrow.

35
00:02:34,760 --> 00:02:35,920
I can just push him away.

36
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:39,520
What's the matter?

37
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:46,360
How could it be?

38
00:02:48,760 --> 00:02:49,680
I thought you said

39
00:02:50,480 --> 00:02:51,920
the arrow was shot from south?

40
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:55,760
I didn't say there were
no arrows from north.

41
00:03:06,816 --> 00:03:09,644
=Fortune Writer=

